resources.string:
All numbers are clickable.

 Single click provides expected action:
 - main clock: start/pause;
 - shot clock: start new or switch to short possession (if enabled in settings);
 - score: increase value by 2;
 - period: set new period and set to default corresponding values;
 - fouls and timeouts: increase value by one.

 Long press:
 - main and shot clock: allows to change current value;
 - other number elements: will set zero state;
 - team names: set new team name.
 * Long click actions work only if main time on pause.

